Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

snippet.description:
#Vrusshabha #Mohanlal #Diwali2025 #VrusshabhaTeaser #RoarOfVrusshabha #ConnekktMedia #BalajiTelefilms #AbishekSVyasStudios #AashirvadCinemas

Welcome to the World of Vrusshabha.

A unique story brought to life through an unforgettable cinematic experience for global audiences. With Mohanlal playing a king for the very first time in a bilingual epic, Vrusshabha is a film that promises to stay with you long after you leave the theatre. Vrusshabha is a grand Pan Indian film shot simultaneously in Malayalam and Telugu, and dubbed in Hindi and Kannada.

Janmo Ka Ye Bandhan
Pyar Se Joda Hai Rabb Ne
Preet Ka Daman 
Hai Nayi Rasme, Nayi Kasame
Nayi Uljhan
Hont Hai Khamosh
Lekin Keh Rahi Dhakan

Tere naam ke harf ki tasbeeh ko, saanson
Ke gale ka haar kiya, duniya bhooli aur sirf
tujhe haan sirf tujhe hi pyar kiya

Tum jeet gaye hum hare, 
Tum jeet gaye hum hare, hum hare aur tum jeete
Mere dil ki dil se tauba, dil se tauba mere Dil ki
Dil ki tauba hai dil ab pyar dobara na hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Humne dhadkan dhadkan karke,
dil tere dil se jod liya
Ankhon ne ankhen padh padh ke, 
tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Tujhe pyaar kiya toh tu hi bata, hum ne kya koi jurm kiya
Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara

Bol kaffara kya hoga

snippet.title: Rekka Rekka | Bison Kaalamaadan | Dhruv Vikram | Mari Selvaraj | Nivas K Prasanna | Arivu | Vedan

Whistle : Nikhil Mathew

snippet.description:
‚ÄòUnderground‚Äô by Dhanda Nyoliwala is here ‚Äì a powerful anthem of grit, hustle, and staying true to your roots. Watch now!

#Underground #Kohram #DhandaNyoliwala

Asst: Angelina
Costumes: Khwaish

Music release inquiries: contact.vyrlregional@umusic.com

Lyrics

Ho bajne ke goli hore poore poore chances
Viprit challe jamma circumstances
Past ke sin meri aankhya aage are
Bola present baithe baithe future tenses
O famous ke hoye r rutba sabke radak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
 
Ho din mai ha delhi din dhalde dubai
Jyada lava na dimag kra dil n jo kahi
R ye kal ke chalaru dekhi success nyi
Dev duniya misal jinki ha bande vahi
Mahre marne ke bde karr jaap baliye
Dusmani thodi ni bairi lakh baliye
Nhi ghatda yo chadta he rahna chori r
Mahri hate gaane dono ka graph baliye
Yo ghalna gal mai he mahre jo fanda latak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
 
Hatha mai rolly hai koke barette pai
Babu n  naaj r poora hai bete pai
Loga ke kahne p kar na bharosa tu
Mahra to bera r paate hai fette pai
Khet mai baithe ha phone p bollywood
Day one t vision m yara ke Hollywood
Dikhn mai anpad ha padke nai baithe ha
Garcia marquez ka 100 years of solitude
Gyan na de bhai mahra to bheja satak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
 
Aim focus pe mera kde door ni hoya hai
Paisa itna kamaya ke gurur ni hoya hai
Tere nain r nashile esa jaadu kar chori
Desi daru ka bhi kde jo suroor ni hoya hai
Kri julfa flip ban gigi hadid
Tera mukh dekhya bina chand dekhe bni eid
Log soch mai pde hai kis tarah bni hogi

Tere chehre ki kasis or giza pyramid
Tene dekh dekh chori chore ka dil yo dhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
Ye chore underground hore r mudda poora bhadak rya hai
 
Chore chale underground we never go down
Chore chale underground we never go down

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, ‚ÄúDude, same!‚Äù 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that‚Äôs funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you‚Äôre laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you‚Äôre caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it‚Äôs a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

Directed by Sujeeth, with music by Thaman S, and produced by DVV Danayya under DVV Entertainment, this high-octane gangster action drama is all set to hit theatres on 25th September 2025.

This video is made only for showcasing the editing skills of the individual.

Witness the ultimate action spectacle, breathtaking visuals, and Pawan Kalyan‚Äôs unstoppable screen presence that will set the box office on fire!

‚ùØ‚ùØ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

~ Lyrics ~ Vikram Sarkar - Naam Chale
Ghumti game chle 
Goj me fame chle 
Note jit na chale 
Yaar ka name chle bby 
Gail me mam chle 
Top ka time chle 
Note jit naa chaale 
Yaar ka time chale bby 

Dunia me horya shor dekh 
Tu krke chori gor dekh 
Meri k dekhe tu ankhyan me 
Tu bas vikram Ki taur dekh 
Na ger pyar k fande ne 
Na puch tu chori dhnde ne 
M gailyan rakhu 4 mistri 
Khol k dhr de bande ne 
Virodhi sehm chle 
Kadhta bhem chle 
Note jit na chaale 
Yaar ka name chle bby 

Khulle se khate na pdte hisaban me 
Masti me rehte hum rehte na yadan me 
1 life mili bby jee re swadan me 
Talented balak na pdte vivaadan me 
Tu dekh yaar auda 
Se ped na samjhe paudha 
Mne kehke system paade se 
Firr tu bby k sauda 
Bairi ne rakhu koda 
Dharti lgwadu goda 
Chal manya thoda ghaat krya 
Par kaam krya naa boda bby 
Vibe na same chle 
Mind me aim chle 
Note jit naa chaale 
Yaar ka name chale bby
